---
---
<section class="section why-us" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-visual animate-fadeUp">
        <div class="why-main-card">
          <div class="badge badge-gold" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Why 50,000 Families Trust Us</div>
          <h3 class="why-main-title">
            We Don't Just Move Things.<br/><span class="text-gold">We Move Lives.</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="why-main-desc">
            Every box we pack holds memories. Every piece of furniture carries years of life. That's why PackersHub treats every single move as if it's our own family's home being relocated.
          </p>
          <div class="why-stats-grid">
            <div class="why-stat-box">
              <div class="why-stat-val">₹3,999</div>
              <div class="why-stat-lab">Starting Price</div>
            </div>
            <div class="why-stat-box">
              <div class="why-stat-val">24/7</div>
              <div class="why-stat-lab">Support Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="why-stat-box">
              <div class="why-stat-val">0%</div>
              <div class="why-stat-lab">Hidden Charges</div>
            </div>
            <div class="why-stat-box">
              <div class="why-stat-val">100%</div>
              <div class="why-stat-lab">Insured Moves</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-badge-float animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
          <span style="font-size:24px;">🏆</span>
          <div>
            <div class="why-badge-num">Best Movers</div>
            <div class="why-badge-text">South India 2024</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="section-tag">Our Advantage</div>
        <h2 class="heading-lg" style="margin-bottom:40px;">What Makes <span class="text-gradient-gold">PackersHub</span> Different</h2>

        <div class="why-features">
          <div class="why-feature">
            <div class="why-feature-icon" style="background:rgba(21,71,160,0.1);">🔒</div>
            <div class="why-feature-body">
              <div class="why-feature-title">100% Damage-Free Guarantee</div>
              <p class="why-feature-desc">We back every move with our Zero Damage Promise. If anything breaks, we replace it — full stop. No questions asked.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-feature">
            <div class="why-feature-icon" style="background:rgba(201,148,58,0.1);">📡</div>
            <div class="why-feature-body">
              <div class="why-feature-title">Real-Time GPS Tracking</div>
              <p class="why-feature-desc">Know exactly where your belongings are at every moment. Track your truck live on your phone — peace of mind, delivered.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-feature">
            <div class="why-feature-icon" style="background:rgba(139,155,90,0.1);">💰</div>
            <div class="why-feature-body">
              <div class="why-feature-title">Transparent, Fixed Pricing</div>
              <p class="why-feature-desc">The price you're quoted is the price you pay. Zero hidden fees. Zero surprises. Full breakdown provided upfront.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-feature">
            <div class="why-feature-icon" style="background:rgba(232,83,122,0.1);">⚡</div>
            <div class="why-feature-body">
              <div class="why-feature-title">Express Moving Available</div>
              <p class="why-feature-desc">Need to move in 24 hours? We make it happen. Emergency relocation specialists on standby across South India.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-us { background: var(--gray-50); padding: 100px 0; }
  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .why-visual { position: relative; }
  .why-main-card {
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 50px 40px;
    color: var(--white);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-blue);
  }
  .why-main-card::before {
    content: '🏆';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px;
    right: -10px;
    font-size: 140px;
    opacity: 0.06;
  }
  .why-main-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .text-gold { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .why-main-desc {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .why-stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .why-stat-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .why-stat-box:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .why-stat-val {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
  .why-stat-lab { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  .why-badge-float {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -24px;
    right: -24px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .why-badge-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue-700);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .why-badge-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-600); font-family: var(--font-ui); }

  .why-features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
  .why-feature {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .why-feature:hover {
    border-color: var(--blue-300);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(21,71,160,0.1);
    transform: translateX(6px);
  }
  .why-feature-icon {
    width: 52px; height: 52px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
  }
  .why-feature-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .why-feature-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
    .why-badge-float { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-us { padding: 60px 0; }
    .why-main-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .why-badge-float { position: static; margin-top: 24px; width: fit-content; }
  }
</style>
